                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "\"Well, you;re pretty good! But it's time for me to show you how to really play at cards!\"",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:rgb(204, 191, 173)"
                      ],
